This paper deals with video analysis and natural language processing, which are both relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with action localization, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.CV and cs.CL, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.MM.
